  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE MISSISSIPPI VIOLENT CRIME TASK FORCE TO EXAMINE VIOLENT CRIME CLEARANCE RATES AND RECOMMEND POLICIES THAT IMPROVE PUBLIC SAFETY AND JUSTICE OUTCOMES; TO STATE LEGISLATIVE FINDINGS AND PURPOSE; TO SET FORTH THE DUTIES OF THE TASK FORCE, ITS MEMBERSHIP, ORGANIZATION AND ADMINISTRATION; TO REQUIRE THE TASK FORCE TO REPORT TO THE LEGISLATURE; TO PROVIDE THAT THE TASK FORCE SHALL CONTINUE IN EXISTENCE UNTIL OTHERWISE PROVIDED BY LAW; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
